OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775628243
OL,3,CTributes paid to teenager who died in
OL,4,Cstabbing as fundraisers set up
OL,6,FA teenager who died in a stabbing in
OL,7,FKent has been described as a "truly
OL,8,Floveable soul".
OL,10,FPolice officers were called at 2.04am
OL,11,Fon Friday (3 April) to reports of a
OL,12,Fserious assault in Belmont Road,
OL,13,FWhitstable.
OL,15,FPatrols and paramedics went to the
OL,16,Fscene where 19-year-old father, Ashton
OL,17,FHarrington, was found with stab wounds.
OL,19,FHe died at the scene. Officers believe
OL,20,Fhe was known to his attackers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
