PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775628243
OL,3,CTributes paid to teenager who died in
OL,4,Cstabbing as fundraisers set up
OL,6,FA fundraiser has been set up to help
OL,7,Fcover the costs of his funeral.
OL,9,FA statement on the fundraising page
OL,10,Fsaid: "We are heartbroken to share the
OL,11,Fdevastating loss of our beloved Ashton
OL,12,FHarrington, taken from us far too soon
OL,13,Fat just 19 years old.
OL,15,F"Ashton was a truly loveable soul -
OL,16,Ffull of life, with an infectious smile
OL,17,Fand laugh that could light up any room.
OL,19,F"He meant everything to his family and
OL,20,Ffriends, and his loss has left a hole
OL,21,Fthat can never be filled."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775628243
OL,3,CTributes paid to teenager who died in
OL,4,Cstabbing as fundraisers set up
OL,6,FIt continued: "As this tragedy was
OL,7,Fcompletely unexpected, Ashton did not
OL,8,Fhave life insurance, and his family is
OL,9,Fnow facing the overwhelming burden of
OL,10,Ffuneral costs during an already
OL,11,Funimaginably difficult time.
OL,13,F"We are raising funds to help support
OL,14,FAshton's parents and brothers, easing
OL,15,Fsome of the financial pressure so they
OL,16,Fcan focus on grieving and remembering
OL,17,Fthe incredible person Ashton was."
OL,19,FThe organisers thanked people for
OL,20,Ftheir "kindness, love, and support
OL,21,Fduring this heartbreaking time".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
