CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775628243
OL,3,CTributes paid to teenager who died in
OL,4,Cstabbing as fundraisers set up
OL,6,F"One choice has countless consequences
OL,7,Fand destroys so many lives...
OL,9,F"We love you Ashton you are so loved."
OL,11,FDetectives would like to speak to
OL,12,FKieron Barnes and Tobias Agbaje who
OL,13,Fthey say may have information that
OL,14,Fcould assist the investigation.
OL,16,FAnyone who knows of their whereabouts
OL,17,Fis being asked to call Kent Police on
OL,18,F999 quoting 46/52649/26.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
